      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MILITARY MERIT (1) is a quality entire who has amassed two wins and six minor placings from eight starts this time in work. Produced another fine effort last start when he finished second over 2050m at Port Pirie, beaten a nose. A nice draw on the front line should ensure a cosy run. This doesn't look as hard so he is sure to prove tough to beat. TINEY (6) won at this track two runs ago before finishing third at his latest appearance over 2050m at Port Pirie, beaten 4 metres. Finds a nice race and can play a major role. JANES GEM (3) disappointed last time when eighth over 1800m at this track. Can turn things around. IMA DESTROYER (4) cannot be left out after solid recent performances, the latest a sound fourth at this track over 2230m.",
